name: AngelMaker
description:
AngelMaker is a mega merge of several of the most popular anime-style models available. It is a combination of, in no particular order:

  • BloodOrangeMix

  • AbyssOrangeMix

  • SlimeX

  • Counterfeit 2.5

  • GrapefruitHentai

  • Maple Syrup v1

It is capable of both SFW and NSFW generations as well as both male and female characters.

Feel free to use any anime VAE you want, I have had success with the BloodOrangeMix VAE, Anything v4.5 VAE, and Maple Syrup VAE. All produce extremely similar results and work very well.

It is highly recommended that you use this model with, at minimum, the bad_prompt_version2 TI, bad-artist TI, and bad-image-v2-39000 TI. EasyNegative and bad-hands-5 can also help but aren't required.

As always, keep your negative prompts simple! Check the example pictures to see some ideal negative prompts.
